Class DependencyManager

java.lang.Object
  jade.tools.ascml.dependencymanager.DependencyManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
ModelChangedListener
public class DependencyManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ModelChangedListener

This class is responsible for updating the status of all models. It has to main parts: The FunctionalStateController and the DependencyStateController

Author:
